text: Agnieszka Tomczak (born 29 May 1975 in Bydgoszcz) is a Polish rower. She completed in the women's single scull event in the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== == External links == * * * * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bydgoszcz
